g.aria-label: sustain: amplitude at which to hold the note after decay
attack: rate and target amplitude of note initiation
decay: rate at which to alter amplitude to sustain level
Select desired part from dropdown menu, press load part button and wait for conductor to begin.If rehearsing alone, select desired mark from dropdown and press Goto mark.

path.aria-label: Defines how to play notes as they pass the playback line.Notes that appear on duration line begin from current sustain level.
